data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Single Family Home is nestled on a tranquil Cul-de-Sac street where you can say goodbye to through traffic and hello to peace and privacy.    This home has been thoughtfully updated to meet today's standards and offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. From the moment you arrive, you'll be captivated by its inviting curb appeal and the promise of a peaceful, friendly neighborhood.    From fresh interior paint throughout to sleek fixtures, you'll find contemporary touches throughout. Natural light pours in, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.    The 2021 remodeled kitchen is a Chef's dream, boasting stainless steel appliances, Shaker Cabinets and Quartz countertops with plenty of room and ample cabinet space. It's perfect for both daily meals and entertaining.    The spacious primary bedroom features an ensuite bath that was remodeled in 2023, ensuring your privacy and convenience. It's your own personal retreat.    The two additional bedrooms are generously sized and perfect for children, guests, or a home office. The laundry room is conveniently located off the kitchen.    Step outside to your private backyard. With the covered patio, it's a fantastic place to relax, play, or host BBQs. Enjoy the Fruit trees including Lemon, Mulberry, Peach, Apricot, Loquat, Cherimoya and Calamondin.    Additional significant upgrades include new forced air furnace and all ducting replaced, dual pane vinyl windows, electrical panel upgraded to 200 AMP including all new wiring throughout the house, new roof installed in 2015, new water heater installed in 2020, new vinyl plank flooring, front lawn automatic sprinklers.    The two-car attached garage provides ample storage and convenience.    Enjoy nearby parks, shopping, dining, and entertainment options, all within a short drive.    Easy access to major commuter routes, making your work commute a breeze.    This is a home where lasting memories are made. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! Schedule a showing today and discover the lifestyle this charming single-family home has to offer. Your future begins here.
